item.description: Collaboration with the International Chant Academy In May, Marsja successfully collaborated with the International Chant Academy in the USA, giving an online lecture and two practical sessions as part of their Hands on With Hildegard lecture series.
Marsja Mudde Muziek: experienced in giving experience Experienced in giving experience is the motto of Marsja Mudde Muziek and what Marsja stands for as a person and musician.
